messageBody:
We have 247 members today. Just wanted to remind everyone that I set
up a brief poll some weeks back in an attempt to gauge how members are
using quicksript and how long they have used it. I have 14 answers on
question 1 and 11 on question 2. If you have not answered the
question, please take a minute to answer them.

Thanks
